        <p class="section-sub white" style="margin:0 auto;">A structured, transparent, and highly personalised investment process — designed to maximise your returns while managing risk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="wm-steps">
        <div class="wm-step reveal-up">
          <div class="wm-step-icon step-icon-teal">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-pen"></i>
            <span class="wm-step-num">01</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Profile & Discovery</h4>
          <p>We begin by understanding you — your goals, timeline, risk tolerance, existing assets, and long-term financial aspirations through a structured discovery session.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wm-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="wm-step reveal-up d1">
          <div class="wm-step-icon step-icon-violet">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i>
            <span class="wm-step-num">02</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Strategy Design</h4>
          <p>Your dedicated advisor designs a bespoke investment strategy — selecting the ideal mix of asset classes, geographies, and instruments aligned to your profile.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wm-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="wm-step reveal-up d2">
          <div class="wm-step-icon step-icon-gold">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i>
            <span class="wm-step-num">03</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Portfolio Launch</h4>
          <p>Your portfolio goes live with precision execution — institutional-grade order routing, optimal entry points, and full transaction transparency from day one.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wm-step-connector"></div>
        <div class="wm-step reveal-up d3">
          <div class="wm-step-icon step-icon-coral">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i>
            <span class="wm-step-num">04</span>
          </div>
          <h4>Monitor & Rebalance</h4>
          <p>AI monitors your portfolio 24/7, while your advisor meets regularly to review performance, rebalance allocations, and refine strategy as markets evolve.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

